ZH: 我们需要清理一下这条沟。
EN: We need to clean out this ditch.

ZH: 这个沟里面有很多垃圾。
EN: There is a lot of garbage in this ditch.

ZH: 沟里的水很浑浊。
EN: The water in the ditch is very muddy.

ZH: 这座村庄的沟渠需要修理。
EN: The ditches in this village need repairing.

ZH: 经常有人将垃圾扔进沟里。
EN: People often throw trash into the ditch.

ZH: 农民们在田里挖了一个排水沟。
EN: The farmers dug a drainage ditch in the field.

ZH: 她被困在一个深水沟里。
EN: She was trapped in a deep ditch.

ZH: 这条沟是由雨水形成的。
EN: This ditch was formed by rainwater.

ZH: 沟的两边长满了野草。
EN: The banks of the ditch are covered with wild grass.

ZH: 生长在沟边的植物非常茂盛。
EN: The plants growing on the edge of the ditch are very lush.

ZH: 他们沿着沟边走到了村庄。
EN: They walked along the ditch to the village.

ZH: 沟边的土壤质量很好。
EN: The soil quality along the ditch is very good.

ZH: 路边有一个排水沟，防止水积聚。
EN: There is a drainage ditch on the side of the road to prevent water accumulation.

ZH: 这条小河在这里形成了一个很长的沟。
EN: This small river has formed a long ditch here.

ZH: 沟的底部布满了石子。
EN: The bottom of the ditch is covered with stones.

ZH: 昨天暴雨导致山坡上形成了一条新的沟。
EN: Yesterday's heavy rain caused a new ditch to form on the hillside.

ZH: 农民们用挖掘机开挖了一个大型水沟。
EN: The farmers used an excavator to dig a large water ditch.

ZH: 这条沟的宽度约为两米。
EN: The width of this ditch is about two meters.

ZH: 这个地区有很多用于排水的沟渠。
EN: There are many drainage ditches in this area.

ZH: 沟里的水流很快，不容易淤塞。
EN: The water in the ditch flows quickly and is not easy to clog.
